Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.33,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:03:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.43,0:03:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.07,0:03:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after\NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves\N caught up in the turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while Zoro, Usopp and Brook get \Ncaptured by Hordy at the Ryugu Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She broke... She broke my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:04:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What don't I just destroy \Neverything altogether?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, he gave me a lot of trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Hachi, Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was the true power of the drug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:41.72,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"A Surprising Confession! The Truth \NBehind the Assassination of Otohime!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are almost at the plaza! Hurry up, Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm here-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jimbei-sama! Megalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm here-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna see the \NPrincess get hurt, freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's take her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:47.24,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}CONCHCORDE PLAZA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have quite an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.72,0:06:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a view!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.94,0:06:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Mamboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Ryuboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Fukaboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did the pirates manage that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princes were winning by far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, the tables \Nhave turned against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wanna fight some more-zugon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much! Don't get so heated up! Or I'm gonna\N become a piece of dried squid-ch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers of the army. The ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the royal family. There is no one \Nleft in this country, who can fight us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What unbelievable power!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be!\N Those powers are fake-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't really matter if it \Nenables them to take over the country!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy, let's put them to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Burn them alive!\N--No, impale them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:07:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish a terrible death on those who lack \Npride and look to coexist with the humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show the audience!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard from Decken's crew yet,\N with regards to Shirahoshi's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no point in doing \Nthis if we can't lure her here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything to our sister!\N She won't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.82,0:07:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't harm you in any way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that I don't know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the Mermaid with that troublesome\N power so I want to be rid of her the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Shirahoshi and \NJimbei got caught in a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama! Brothers-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught the two that I \Nconcerned about most, all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is too good to be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.67,0:08:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't have to go through\N this if I hadn't been fooled...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's done is done so never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here as I thought, Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.43,0:08:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I liked you back when you were a wild man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you, Hordy? \NYou look so different from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Boss Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he left the island \Nafter he quit the Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Princess Shirahoshi had\N been kidnapped by Straw Hat Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Boss Jimbei rescue her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everyone that I wanted to see is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was easier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only concern now is \Nwhat the Straw Hats will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.64,0:09:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I assume they're desperately looking\N for a way in to the Ryugu Palace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they make it here after \Nthey find their friends dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're totally ready to ambush them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 30,000 human slaves we've \Ncaught in the sea over the past month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And 70,000 Fish-Men who know how to use arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.10,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They moved here from the \Nclosed Fish-Man District.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...100,000 outlaws altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a few female and child slaves\N who can't fight, outside the plaza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:12:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take care of them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll soon have more human slaves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, 100,000 of you islanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fools are a dishonor to our\N race so vacate your houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can either drop dead or run.\N Think about what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horsing around in public...\N You kids have no class at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you for a \Nlong time. What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to say one thing to you \Nsince you're at the height of your glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Sharley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my prevision, a man \Nwill destroy the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it me that you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who will destroy the island is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell what the Straw Hat\Nboy will do specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My point is that it's not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who determines the \Nfate of the Fish-Man Island is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not you, Hordy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see! Madam's previsions are accurate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means Hordy will never\N reign over the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Sharley!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Madam!\N--How could he do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that, Sharley?\N What do you have against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, when I was a kid,\N everybody in the Fish-Man District
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.59,0:14:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may have looked\N up to your brother Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then we seized power.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, the name "Arlong Pirates" is \Nnothing but a symbol to unite us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even need the \Nname "Arlong" anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only man who can break the whole country\N to its foundation and rebuild it, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...me! Because I have enough power to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look how powerful I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the power that I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started this whole thing 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concerning the late Queen of the Ryugu\N Kingdom, who you fools still love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:16:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime was killed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the human then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you not notice it, idiots?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day before that fateful \Nday 10 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I would do anything if I \Ncan make some big money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this real money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a half of it. You can have\N the rest after you finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just this is enough to drink \Nall day for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so easy. Even a child can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.64,0:17:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, don't let anyone notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Put out the fire!\N--Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Protect the royal family!\N--Put out the fire now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otohime-sama has been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.31,0:17:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give me the rest of that money now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set fire to those \Nsignatures like you told me to!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:18:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna make a run for it \Nalready so give me the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who killed our queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime was killed by a human!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody got fooled completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed Queen Otohime!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was annoying. \NDon't you think so, Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She begged everyone not to \Nseek revenge against humans
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to become friends with them instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was bugging me because she \Nalmost accomplished her goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I wouldn't be satisfied\N with just killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, your mother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...someone who deserved death!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such a thing to the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I came up with an idea \Nto make the best of her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would allow me to stoke\N the hatred towards humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that citizens of the \NFish-Man Island once had
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and destroy the islanders' stupid \Ndream along with Otohime - all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd point the finger at a \Nhuman for killing Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I blamed it on a human, I knew that the \Nislanders will get pissed off at humans again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it turned out that you all got \Nfooled by my trick exactly as I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was worth killing! Right, Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother was not murdered by a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, her kinsman, did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, standing in front of you now, killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.86,0:21:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, everyone on the \NFish-Man Island came together
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and built a mysterious \Ngiant ship called Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason remains a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.83,0:21:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a leftover from the past now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.08,0:21:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me touch it with my right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Decken, what are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is it? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pain of heartbreak will never go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.45,0:22:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wh-What's going on?!\N--Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm throwing the Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.25,0:22:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.55,0:22:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is half the size \Nof the Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.93,0:22:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means if it hits the island,\N not just Shirahoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the whole island will be shattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't run or hide from me anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.94,0:22:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi has no choice but to \Nstay with me in my heart forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn in hell with the island!\N Goodbye my sweet Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:23:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.71,0:23:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi continues to fulfill her \Npromise to her mother, Otohime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy ridicules her and \Ncommences Neptune's execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The despairing citizens call out \Nthe name of their last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.06,0:23:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And their voice resounds \Nthroughout Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.06,0:23:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shirahoshi's Tears!\N Luffy Finally Shows Up!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.73,0:23:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
